  "detailed_description": "<h1>Update Notes</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/2b7d2f07ce92281e65aaf9f212d7bb00.avif?t=1724753525\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Take on the role of an adventurer of various classes, form a party and raid those dungeons with friends, the more the merrier. Steal from poor (?) monsters, take items back home and make a fortune!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SINGLE PLAYER OR NETWORK CO-OP</h2>Play it solo or work together with your friends to conquer the dungeons. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/8e8e426fe2f92eb519f255bafe7fe7d8.poster.avif?t=1724753525\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/8e8e426fe2f92eb519f255bafe7fe7d8.webm?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/8e8e426fe2f92eb519f255bafe7fe7d8.mp4?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Offline single player or <strong>online co-op</strong> up to 8 players.<br></li><li> Does NOT support same-machine, split-screen, couch co-op, remote-play together.<br></li><li> No friends? No problem! Add BOTs player to help you spice up the adventure.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FAST-PACED SKILL-BASED GAMEPLAY</h2>Master combat mechanic of each class, learn characteristics of each enemy and boss.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/35f219607a10782c32c7abd4a8ff931f.poster.avif?t=1724753525\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/35f219607a10782c32c7abd4a8ff931f.webm?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/35f219607a10782c32c7abd4a8ff931f.mp4?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/b5a3ffb1fc24b14243eb8ccfe00fe0b4.poster.avif?t=1724753525\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/b5a3ffb1fc24b14243eb8ccfe00fe0b4.webm?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/b5a3ffb1fc24b14243eb8ccfe00fe0b4.mp4?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>AND DON'T FORGET TO LOOT ALL THE ITEMS!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/d403ffbbdba18b1b8f86afd3cd065a28.poster.avif?t=1724753525\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/d403ffbbdba18b1b8f86afd3cd065a28.webm?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/d403ffbbdba18b1b8f86afd3cd065a28.mp4?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAKE NEXT RUN STRONGER</h2>Make money, upgrade your skill and equipment, repeat, until you become a master adventurer!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/b72e3652252b30e3b7e9ff3de1747969.poster.avif?t=1724753525\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/b72e3652252b30e3b7e9ff3de1747969.webm?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/b72e3652252b30e3b7e9ff3de1747969.mp4?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NO FRIEND? NO PROBLEM!</h2>Never be lonely on the adventure, add those little BOT players to spice things up.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/bda71c9e5fb5f030539b5cebd088a87d.poster.avif?t=1724753525\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/bda71c9e5fb5f030539b5cebd088a87d.webm?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228320/extras/bda71c9e5fb5f030539b5cebd088a87d.mp4?t=1724753525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
